{"type": "article", "id": 28282, "title": "冰激凌包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-16T06:40:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140701Oyde6usULSxXAoBl.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>甜甜的冰激凌当然要搭配甜美的设计：在 <a href=\"http://www.estudioyeye.com/\">Estudio Yeyé</a> 为墨西哥品牌 La luz del Día 设计的包装上，你可以找到仿佛正在慢慢融化的冰激凌球和点缀用的多彩碎屑。这些简化的图案搭配大胆的配色不规则地出现在包装上，为 80 多年的老品牌注入了一股新潮的感觉。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140658YoR4AxtbPO5HBlqu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140659tuKo5Hi9mGf0bgEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140659u1vfeBPLq0ycX2NG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140700Ufv6CcDZlKuxV5rw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}